76
00:03:03,826 --> 00:03:04,766
they get better at the game,

77
00:03:04,766 --> 00:03:06,807
they come up with new tips and tricks,

78
00:03:06,807 --> 00:03:08,607
find bugs and exploits.

79
00:03:08,607 --> 00:03:11,548
And as they do that, the way the game is played changes.

80
00:03:11,548 --> 00:03:13,369
But traditional AI doesn't.

81
00:03:13,369 --> 00:03:14,749
Traditional AI remains static,

82
00:03:14,749 --> 00:03:17,090
