92
00:03:36,543 --> 00:03:38,465
and we're learning behaviors from the players

93
00:03:38,465 --> 00:03:41,267
and letting them train the AI that's in the game.

94
00:03:41,748 --> 00:03:44,790
Now the cool thing about these shadow fighters is that they're not superhuman.

95
00:03:44,790 --> 00:03:48,692
They have all the same limitations and restrictions, they make the same mistakes that people do.

96
00:03:48,692 --> 00:03:52,775
