00:27:12,074 --> 00:27:14,275
It gives us sort of the way that humans fail

558
00:27:14,275 --> 00:27:16,096
at this particular task.

559
00:27:16,096 --> 00:27:17,997
Some humans have tunnel vision and they only focus

560
00:27:17,997 --> 00:27:20,459
on what's happening right in the center of focus.

561
00:27:20,459 --> 00:27:21,740
And if we record this kind of data,

562
00:27:21,740 --> 00:27:24,721
that would allow us to capture that kind of human failing.

563
00:27:27,952 --> 00:27:30,874
So the other piece of the puzzle is heuristics.

564
00:27:30,874 --> 00:27:32,295
So basically, one thing that we want

565
00:27:32,295 --> 00:27:33,896
to be able to do with a system like this

