00:28:07,906 --> 00:28:10,448
in the current situation, we can use this heuristic value

579
00:28:10,448 --> 00:28:11,830
as well as the other world state value

580
00:28:11,830 --> 00:28:12,831
to select it correctly.

581
00:28:13,231 --> 00:28:16,092
