582
00:28:16,092 --> 00:28:18,714
we can see, okay, what did I do in a situation

583
00:28:18,714 --> 00:28:22,475
where my enemy was blocking low a lot?

584
00:28:22,475 --> 00:28:25,337
And it also works, obviously, for the cases

585
00:28:25,337 --> 00:28:27,878
when a player doesn't do anything

586
00:28:27,878 --> 00:28:30,519
or isn't even sensitive to that kind of adaptation.

